ime I have learned lots of random, useless information about the chao garden. This video covers 50 chao garden facts that are mostly useless, although a lot of them are quite fun and worth knowing about even if they don't really help you raise your chao. This video covers the original Sonic Adventure on the dreamcast, Sonic Adventure DX, Sonic Adventure 2 on the dreamcast, the Sonic Adventure 2 battle re-releases and even the tiny chao garden on the gameboy advance.\n\nThank you to Chao Island, VideoGameClipCollect, and Chao Professor for all publishing information that helped me make this video! Also thank you to my mod/admin team who helped me come up with some of the facts for this video!\n\nEDIT: \n#36 is actually a feature added by chao world extended and not in the regular game (thanks exant for the clarification)\n\nSongs:\nWindmill Isle - Sonic Unleashed\nDragon Road (Day) - Sonic Unleashed\nChao Race Theme - Sonic Adventure\nTheme of Chao - Sonic Adventure\nComfort Zone - Sonic Mania\n\n#chaogarden #sonicadventure #sonicadventure2","commandRuns":[{"startIndex":55,"length":12,"onTap":{"innertubeCommand":{"clickTrackingParams":"CBgQ040EGAYiEwiHv7TCpIiUAxVrvisGHd1iDdXKAQQfzXpb","commandMetadata":{"webCommandMetadata":{"url":"https://www.youtube.com/channel/UCWM2eoCSEO3olwH0FonfAXA/join","webPageType":"WEB_PAGE_TYPE_UNKNOWN","rootVe":83769}},"urlEndpoint":{"url":"https://www.youtube.com/channel/UCWM2eoCSEO3olwH0FonfAXA/join","nofollow":true}}},"onTapOptions":{"accessibilityInfo":{"accessibilityLabel":"YouTube Channel Link: @Choa"}}},{"startIndex":94,"length":13,"onTap":{"innertubeCommand":{"clickTrackingParams":"CBgQ040EGAYiEwiHv7TCpIiUAxVrvisGHd1iDdVIuv6386G0qaCCAcoBBB_Nels=","commandMetadata":{"webCommandMetadata":{"url":"https://www.youtube.com/redirect?event=video_description\u0026redir_token=QUFFLUhqbng3Q29HTS1VTEVsZkFDTGF5RXlGc0FxZFpOZ3xBQ3Jtc0ttMlprOEJBMktFUkNYT1R1bDI2ZnNoZzkyREFGR3M1dU94N0ZDa05XaWlLTFhZU3NtNmo5QkdjUjRkUE5BRnRySUN4MjVGVzNQTW1QdnRXWFVadFA